	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You could do the same with whatever method you're using to run homebrew (PowerPak, other dev cart). Disable CIC, plug the PowerPak/devcart in, run a dumper ROM (which doesn't exist, yet), hotswap Zelda in and let the dumper ROM transfer WRAM over the cable. IDK if there's any chance that hotswapping might corrupt WRAM though...

		

		</td>
